        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1116123409" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer56891309006308804">This has quickly moved up to become one of my favorite Shakespeare play that I&apos;ve read. It has a fairytale quality to it that I adored. And it definitely feels wintery which I loved. <br/><br/>It has an interesting mix of tragedy and comedy, with a romantic ending, which reminds me a lot of <i>The Tempest</i> (another of my favorites).<br/>Very pleased to have read this one, and I can&apos;t wait to discuss it in lecture!</span>
  <span id="freeText56891309006308804" style="display:none">This has quickly moved up to become one of my favorite Shakespeare play that I've read. It has a fairytale quality to it that I adored. And it definitely feels wintery which I loved. <br /><br />It has an interesting mix of tragedy and comedy, with a romantic ending, which reminds me a lot of <i>The Tempest</i> (another of my favorites).<br />Very pleased to have read this one, and I can't wait to discuss it in lecture!</span>
